Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.94,0:00:03.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,公司的业绩蒸蒸日上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:02.05,注释,,0000,0000,0000,,当时游戏界的重大事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.08,0:00:07.02,注释,,0000,0000,0000,,1996年 Nintendo 64（任天堂） 发售 \NGame Boy Pocket（任天堂） 发售
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.74,0:00:07.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,被业界瞩目的年轻社长 木户
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:11.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,时装界的名编辑的高野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:12.39,注释,,0000,0000,0000,,当时游戏界的重大事件 \N1996年 口袋妖怪红•绿（任天堂） 发售 \N电子宠物（万代） 发售
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:15.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,然后格斗游戏江河日下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:19.10,注释,,0000,0000,0000,,当时游戏界的重大事件 \N1996年 樱花大战 （世嘉） 发售 \N1997年 最终幻想7 （史克威尔） 发售
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:18.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,店里也陷入了艰难的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:24.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我没那样说过啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:27.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我也有我的……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.18,0:00:30.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 这段时间 真的不知道要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:31.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:35.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,, 弥生酱 应该去么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:39.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,去她家门前哈 带着礼物哈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:43.01,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你来了啊 小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:46.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,刚才和朋友 玩狗便便好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:48.14,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,喂 店长你有听么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:50.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这里可不能开心的玩狗屎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:51.23,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:52.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不是 才不是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.64,0:00:53.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:56.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 我也差不多要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:57.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,弥生酱还在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我一会儿和后藤桑一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:01.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,交女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:04.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,正准备和弥生酱告白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:05.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不就是个恐龙么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:06.84,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,才不是恐龙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:08.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我们看看照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:11.07,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 让你看看 也没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:13.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我带着呢 给你看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.89,0:01:17.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,话说 店长一直是光棍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:20.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,和女生搭不上话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:22.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 不花钱的话就赶紧回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子啊 根本就不是什么复杂的生物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:28.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,只要说想说的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:32.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,对啊对啊 店长的人生 还没有开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:33.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.85,0:01:38.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哇 这里也不能照大头贴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:40.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:42.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:45.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的 这里有股乌贼臭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:45.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:47.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是你才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:48.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:50.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是谁呢 谁谁谁谁谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:53.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:55.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你的妆掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:56.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:57.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,唔哇 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:01:59.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,等下 厕所 厕所在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:01.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:06.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,话说 那个是男厕吧 虽然也能用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:19.69,注释,,0000,0000,0000,,电子宠物 1997年开始 成为社会现象一般的超人气物品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:23.14,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你们 去和她说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:28.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,算了不弄了 麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.80,0:02:31.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不至于吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:35.32,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,话说 看这个 -什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:47.95,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是神马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:51.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,才不想被你们说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.01,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你们自己 不也是在玩电子宠物么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:55.47,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,伦家还素么都米有缩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:59.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,暴力 暴力 -诶 什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:02:59.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:02.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不要笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:06.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:07.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑你妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:10.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,来我家 来我家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:11.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,誘拐 誘拐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:14.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道这里是什么地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:15.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,机厅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:18.83,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,机厅对吧 没有大头贴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,的确是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:22.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你要是想照相去照相馆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:22.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:25.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是想玩游戏的话去家里玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:27.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,傻大帽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:31.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了好了 机厅是玩游戏的地方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:33.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不玩游戏的人就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:35.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了好了 回去吧回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.83,0:03:40.86,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你们也回去了 你们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:42.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是 回去回去… 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,回去回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:46.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我 还没有和弥生…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:47.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦 回去回去回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:50.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,还没有和弥生酱 -弥生酱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:50.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,笑你妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:52.35,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:55.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,四个人手拉手回家了 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:56.81,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,等等 游戏还给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.86,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样说 稍稍让它在店里帮我赚点钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:01.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回去吧 好了 都回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真是世界末日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:14.91,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你也不玩游戏 早点回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的啦 姑且再呆一会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.75,0:05:47.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,在不 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:53.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛这么正式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:59.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不来店里啊 偶尔也来一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:02.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,工作比较忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:06.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样也挺好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:10.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,稍等… 现在有些忙不开 先挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,等下等下 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:18.11,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,能借我些钱么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:26.14,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个 债主催起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:28.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你要多少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:32.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:35.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,500万
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:36.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:40.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:42.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:44.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你只需要这么点钱么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:50.11,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,只有这么点 是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:54.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 现在很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真的… 这种事情拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.23,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:56.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:08.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你最喜欢的季节是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.47,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好选啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在是夏天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:30.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高中二年级啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:40.67,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:45.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,弥生 我只喜欢你的妹妹啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:50.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不 弥生也很有感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我 决定天野了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:53.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,没有小学生角色吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.63,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,小学生太小了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:00.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 来了 看看 来了 来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:01.63,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,天野现在回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:05.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:06.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:11.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,终于 放学后的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:17.79,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,接下来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:20.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你打算谈什么话题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:20.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.75,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,一定要做得万无一失哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:25.71,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,天野是不会想很深问题的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:30.81,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,她是那种阳光开朗的女孩儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:33.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么突然就牵手了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:39.63,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,店长是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:40.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不是 什么啊 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:42.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,天野绝对也想和我接触的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:47.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你只是因为是模拟战略 所以在享受摸女子手的快乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:50.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,很吵啊 小混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:56.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,噢 小希出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:59.14,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,总是出现啊 这个青梅竹马啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:01.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这个孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:04.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,正经过头了 不好对付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:07.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,小希好就好在她的正儿八经啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:09.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,爱操心 管东管西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:11.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 有点像高野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:14.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,像谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:17.56,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,小希
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:18.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.31,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野 你怎么来这了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:23.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这不是好久没过来了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:26.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,结果过来一看 你又在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.95,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个 还不是因为这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我都羡慕你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,被这么多小伙伴簇拥爱戴着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:44.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.07,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.63,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:02.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,没 好久不见 想送送你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:05.81,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:08.20,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,别客气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:11.56,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,最近怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:16.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治 我要是去外国的话 你觉得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:19.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,外国？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这么突然 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:27.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,想去看看外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:30.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊？什么时候出发？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.39,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治 觉得我应该去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:44.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都决定了 我也不能说什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:50.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:55.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么 我说了错话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:59.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,没有 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:01.39,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那 送我到这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:05.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,再… 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:25.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我坐今天末班飞机走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:26.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:29.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,要阻止我的话 只能趁现在了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:37.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 为什么我要阻止你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:43.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我在公园的老地方等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.23,0:12:47.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么 没听到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.03,0:13:16.03,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,学校里流传着一些奇怪的言论哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:21.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,说你要搬走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道是谁乱说的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:30.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:34.19,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:39.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:42.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不先告诉我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:44.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:48.32,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,因为实在无法说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:49.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:52.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我还是希望你能告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,小希
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:02.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,应该要去追她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:25.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野要去外国是真的呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:40.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,因为高野你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:44.84,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,因为是你我才没能说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:48.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:52.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野 我比谁都更喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:01.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,因为不知道自己能不能把这份心意传达给你 所以才一直犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:07.87,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不过被我这种人喜欢 你也很困扰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:09.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:16.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:21.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:23.14,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:34.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我们会一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,因为以前我们从没分开过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:42.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才一直没发现自己的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:47.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不 其实早就发现了 只是不想承认
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:51.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我不想和你分开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:55.39,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我们好不容易 好不容易才互通心意了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:16:00.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你要去外国 骗我的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:04.32,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以请你不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:31.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易我们才坦诚相对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:34.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这不应该才开始才对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:46.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,恩 我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:07.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧把游戏还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:13.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,在店里 要拿自己拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:16.51,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个 你们知道高野在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:19.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,刚才看到她朝机场去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:20.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.96,0:17:22.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,要赶紧找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:24.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:27.20,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:30.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:36.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:38.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:42.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,如果不说的话 我会后悔一生的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.32,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里 高野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:18.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:24.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野 从很久以前 我就……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:26.21,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:15.63,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是高野吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:18.91,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.48,0:19:20.75,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:23.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:28.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:34.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:40.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:00.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,累死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:03.56,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,关店啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟 对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这里的东西都要变成我家的咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:10.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你能挪个地儿吗 不要 不要 等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:12.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,店已经关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:13.86,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你耳朵聋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:16.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这里 这里 来这里 你看看 看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:20.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,至少把软贷款的部分换了吧 什么软贷款啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:43.71,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂 喂 是木户吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:44.67,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:49.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不好意思 之前我借你的钱 打过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:51.07,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:54.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,现在我束手无策了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:58.67,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我不能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:04.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样的话 店会破产的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.14,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说过要守住店的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:11.21,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个是礼治你的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:14.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治 如果你不依靠自己的话 我怎么帮你都是白搭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:17.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我不会借你钱的 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:27.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢 这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:37.95,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:47.22,注释,,0000,0000,0000,,(拿渡边机厅抵债来！)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:51.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,就这样我陷入了孤立境地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:06.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,很烦啊 都说了他不在家了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:08.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,朱理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:12.35,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,已经好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.42,0:22:14.32,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,已经十年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:17.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你来见我老公吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:18.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:20.99,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治和我已经结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.84,0:22:22.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,结婚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:24.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.64,0:22:27.84,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是很遗憾 那个家伙 今天出去了
